description: Exquisitely designed 3-bed, 3.5-bath residence at 22 Liberty, blending timeless elegance with refined European-inspired finishes. Enjoy sweeping Harbor & skyline views from soaring floor-to-ceiling windows and a private terrace. A gracious entry unfolds into an expansive, sunlit living and dining space framed by 10-ft ceilings—ideal for luxurious everyday living & sophisticated entertaining. The chef’s kitchen is a showpiece, featuring a grand waterfall island, Wolf & Miele appliances, Sub-Zero refrigeration, wine storage & sleek custom cabinetry. The primary suite is a serene retreat with a custom walk-in closet & spa-like bath boasting a striking Boffi rain shower and dual fixtures. Secondary bedrooms each offer en-suite baths, with one customized as a stylish home office or guest suite. Other highlights include LED Lutron lighting, 2 garage spaces with EV charger, and private storage. 5-star amenities: 24-hr concierge, fitness center, boardroom, lounge with terrace & coffee station.

exclusions: Dining Room Chandelier. Drapery In Living Room & Bedrooms.Mirror In Half Bath
